 🚦 Market Readiness Verdict Framework

 READY FOR MARKET ✅
All items above checked ✓ (100% completion)

 READY FOR FULL LAUNCH 🟢
- 95% of checklist complete
- All MTO export items ✓
- All security items ✓
- All compliance items ✓
- 10+ pilot schools active
- Support infrastructure operational

 READY FOR SOFT LAUNCH 🟡
- 90% of checklist complete
- Core MTO export functionality ✓
- Payment processing ✓
- Security validation ✓
- 5+ pilot schools active
- Basic support ready

 READY FOR BETA 🟠
- 85% complete
- MTO export working ✓
- Core features functional ✓
- 3 pilot schools active
- Security basics ✓

 MINIMUM VIABLE PRODUCT ⚡
- Phases 0-11 complete
- Students can book lessons
- Instructors see schedules
- GPS tracking consensual
- Basic payment processing
- MTO export functional

 NOT READY ❌
Missing any of:
- MTO export capability
- Payment processing
- PIPEDA compliance
- Offline sync capability
- Security validation
- Multi-language support (EN/FR)

